Warriors are the masters of armed comat and often find themselves as
leaders on the battlefield.  Seasoned warrioris have been known to rally
their troops in combat with powerful battlecries, motiviating their weary
soldiers and allowing them to continue the fight with renewed vigor.

Technical description: Rally gives the warrior and his group members a
bonus to maximum hit points and maximum vitality, as well as a corresponding
boost to current hit points and vitality.  As such, it functions as a both
a buff and a form of regeneration.
